Moodle 1.9 Chat Console Ver. 0.5
================================

Description:
------------

This is a beta version of a gmail/facebook like chat for Moodle 1.9.

It allows two users in a Moodle site chat with each other.

This block was written by Atar + Plus - http://atarplpl.co.il.
Any remarks, information, bugs etc. can be sent to: yedidia@atarplpl.co.il

This block was inspired by a software design made by Israel Open University.
http://www.openu.ac.il

The graphics parts were made by Comverse Ltd.

Installation instructions:
--------------------------

1. Extract the 'chat_console' directory to your moodle 'blocks' directory.
2. Go to 'Notification' in the 'Site Administration' block - it should write
   something about creation of table and let you do some settings.
3. Now you can add the block to your site.

